In [5]:
scatter = (
     Scatter()
     .set_global_opts(title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title='特征 均值-标准差 散点图'), xaxis_opts=opts.AxisOpts(type_='value'))
     .add_xaxis(mean_std['mean'])
     .add_yaxis('train', y_value,
                label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(
                    formatter=JsCode(
                    "function(params){return params.value[2];}"
                    )),
                tooltip_opts=opts.TooltipOpts(
                    formatter=JsCode(
                    "function(params){return params.value[2] + '<br>' + params.value[0] + ' , ' + params.value[1];}"
                    ))
               )
 )
scatter.render_notebook()

heat = (
    HeatMap(init_opts=opts.InitOpts(width='800px',height='800px'))
    .add_xaxis(col)
    .add_yaxis("train", col[::-1], value,
               tooltip_opts=opts.TooltipOpts(
                   formatter=JsCode("function(params){return params.value;}"
                                   )))
        .set_global_opts(
            title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title="特征 相关系数 热力图"),
            visualmap_opts=opts.VisualMapOpts(min_=-1, max_=1, dimension=2, pos_left='70%', pos_top='20%')
       )
)
